---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Recursos — Vibecoding 16">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12">
    <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.22em] text-white/60">RECURSOS</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Herramientas y links</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Base web</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-white/75">
          <li>MDN Web Docs: https://developer.mozilla.org/</li>
          <li>Chrome DevTools: https://developer.chrome.com/docs/devtools/</li>
          <li>Astro: https://astro.build/</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Google (Labs / IA)</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-white/75">
          <li>Google Labs: https://labs.google/</li>
          <li>AI Studio (Gemini): https://aistudio.google.com/</li>
          <li>Vertex AI (overview): https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-white/55" style={{ fontFamily: 'JetBrains Mono, monospace' }}>
          Nota: vamos a ir sumando recursos por clase para que no sea una ensalada.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Diseño</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-white/75">
          <li>Google Fonts: https://fonts.google.com/</li>
          <li>Tailwind: https://tailwindcss.com/</li>
          <li>Accesibilidad (intro): https://www.w3.org/WAI/fundamentals/</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
